    "en": {
      "title": "Sea waves crashing ashore in Galle",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As the sea waves washed ashore towards the land, many places including the Police Station and the Customs Department in Galle Samudra Mawathi were flooded.",
        "Today (02) in the evening, due to the intrusion of sea waves into the terrain, traffic on Galle - Matara main road is blocked due to flood and sand.",
        "Also, it is known that many fishing boats parked on the beach have washed ashore due to the waves and the shore of Samudra Mawatha has also been damaged."
      ],
